.TH GRAFANA-UTIL-STATUS 1 "2026-04-03" "grafana-util 0.7.4" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
grafana\-util\-status \- render shared staged or live project status
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B grafana-util status [\fISUBCOMMAND\fR] [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
render shared project\-wide staged or live status.
.PP
when you need the final gate view for exported artifacts or live Grafana state.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
.B staged
render project status from staged artifacts. Use when: Need the machine\-readable readiness gate for exported files before apply.
.TP
.B live
render project status from live Grafana read surfaces. Use when: Need current Grafana status, optionally deepened with staged context files.
